		    <p>All communications are encrypted using SSL (Secure Socket Layer) technology. The site uses 256-bit 
			SSL certificates provided by independent CA (Certificate Authority), Comodo. Messages exchanged on the 
			web site are encrypted before storage on our servers.</p>
		    
